      Methods in cz.muni.fi.virtualtoolmanager.pubapi.managers that return VirtualizationToolManager 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      VirtualizationToolManager ConnectionManager.connectTo(PhysicalMachine physicalMachine)
      Method that ensures the connection establishment with the required physical machine on which is present the VirtualBox installation with the web server that must be running at the moment when there is made an attempt to establish the connection with the physical machine.
      VirtualizationToolManager ConnectionManager.connectTo(PhysicalMachine physicalMachine, long millis)
      Method that is same as ConnectionManager.connectTo(PhysicalMachine), but with this method is possible to define the time in milliseconds which determine the waiting time between each unsuccessful connection establishment attempt.
